# ClawTalk Assets

This directory contains static assets for the ClawTalk application.

## Structure

```
assets/
├── images/     # Application images
├── icons/      # Custom icons
└── fonts/      # Custom fonts (SF Pro)
```

## Adding Assets

1. Place images in `images/` directory
2. Place custom icons in `icons/` directory
3. Place font files in `fonts/` directory
4. Reference them in `pubspec.yaml` under `flutter.assets`